profile:
Welcome to Mobile Pool & Spa. We've been proudly serving the Lower Mainland since 1999 and are here to provide reliable, honest and solid workmanship to our customers. 

Our Services: Installation and Maintenance Services, Pool and Hot Tub & Spa Maintanence, Service and Repair, Automation and Upgrades. We also specialize in above building in ground pools, installing and repairing Inground Pool Liners, and also sell parts and a wide variety of pool chemicals. Covid 19 – We are following the health and safety protocols as set by the Province of Ontario. Contact us today to set up an appointment.
payment_method: Cash, Cheque, Visa, Mastercard, E transfer, American Express
warranty_terms: Warranty – 1 year on parts and 90 days on our labor
